item.title: CVE-2020-1985|2024-09-16T18:28:43.796Z -- secdo -- secdo
item.description: Incorrect Default Permissions on C:\Programdata\Secdo\Logs folder in Secdo allows local authenticated users to overwrite system files and gain escalated privileges. This issue affects all versions Secdo for Windows.
